== About ==

WeekTimer app for a Raspberry Pi that uses sysfs controlled gpio.


== Build this app ==

First update the submodules, then build it with.

<pre>
qmake
make
</pre>

== Install ==

<pre>
./createdeb.sh
sudo /etc/init.d/monit stop
sudo dpkg -r WeekTimerGPIO
sudo dpkg -i WeekTimerGPIO_*.deb
sudo /etc/init.d/monit start
</pre>


== tzdata ==

If your system is lacking timezone information.
<pre>
sudo dpkg-reconfigure tzdata
</pre>

